#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Indledning"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Repetitive Strain Injury can occur as a result of working with a mouse and "
"keyboard. This utility can be used to remind you to take a break now and "
"then. It displays a random picture from a collection at specified intervals "
"for defined durations. You can configure the pictures to show and lengths of "
"time to show them. You might use the breaks reminders to do some stretching "
"exercises, for example, or as a reminder to walk away from the computer for "
"a while."
msgstr ""
"En belastningsskade er en sygdom som kan forårsages af at arbejde med mus og "
"tastatur. Dette værktøj kan bruges til at påminde dig om at holde en pause "
"af og til. Det viser et tilfældigt billede fra en samling med et angivet "
"interval og med angiven varighed. Du kan indstille billederne som vises og i "
"hvor lang tid de vises. Du kan bruge påmindelserne om pauser for eksempel "
"til at udføre nogle strækkeøvelser, eller som en påmindelse om at gå væk fra "
"computeren en stund."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Logo &rsibreak;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Logotype for &rsibreak;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Logo &rsibreak;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Logotype for &rsibreak;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&rsibreak; was originally written by Tom Albers. Early in the development "
"Bram Schoenmakers joined the project"
msgstr ""
"&rsibreak; blev oprindelig skrevet af Tom Albers. Tidligt i udviklingen gik "
"Bram Schoenmakers med i projektet."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &rsibreak;"
msgstr "Brugen af &rsibreak;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The idea of &rsibreak; is to interrupt you in your work. The intention is to "
"do that in a user-friendly manner. There will be times, though, that it will "
"display itself when you are very busy. The configuration options in "
"&rsibreak; are an effort to allow you to customize the interruptions. In "
"that way we hope you will be able to improve your effectiveness at work "
"while lessening your chances of injury."
msgstr ""
"Idéen bagved &rsibreak; er at afbryde dig når du arbejder. Hensigten er at "
"gøre dette på en brugervenlig måde. Det kommer dog til at findes tilfælde "
"hvor det vises når du er meget optaget. Indstillingsvalgmulighederne i "
"&rsibreak; er et forsøg på at lade dig indstille afbrydelserne. På den måde "
"håber vi at du vil kunne forbedre din effektivitet på arbejdet, mens "
"risikoen for at du kommer ud for skader mindskes."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "After starting, you can see an icon in your tray and you will see a "
#| "welcome pop up. Although the application should be useful with default "
#| "settings, it may be wise to take control by examining the settings. To "
#| "discover and asses the options available, right click on the tray icon; "
#| "in the context menu that appears, select <guilabel>Configure</guilabel>. "
#| "The following chapters contain further configuration information."
msgid ""
"After starting, you can see an icon in your tray and you will see a welcome "
"pop up. Although the application should be useful with default settings, it "
"may be wise to take control by examining the settings. To discover and to "
"obtain an access to the options available, right click on the tray icon; in "
"the context menu that appears, select <guilabel>Configure</guilabel>. The "
"following chapters contain further configuration information."
msgstr ""
"Efter du har startet det, ser du en ikon i statusfeltet og en "
"velkomstmeddelelse dukker op. Selvom programmet kan være nyttigt med "
"standardindstillinger, kan det være passende selv at styre ved at "
"kontrollere indstillingerne. For at opdage og vurdere tilgængelige tilvalg, "
"højreklikkes på ikonen i statusfeltet og vælg <guilabel>Indstil</guilabel> i "
"den sammenhængsafhængige menuen som vises. Følgende kapitel indeholder "
"yderligere indstillingsinformation."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "&rsibreak; statistics"
msgstr "Statistik i &rsibreak;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Left click on the tray icon to see statistics"
msgstr "Venstreklik på ikonen i statusfeltet for at se statistik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you left click on the tray icon you will see some statistics. If you "
"configure &rsibreak; to break at fixed times your idle time will not be "
"measured. In that case, some of the options in the statistics may not be "
"very informative."
msgstr ""
"Når du venstreklikker på ikonen i statusfeltet ser du statistik. Når du har "
"indstillet &rsibreak; til at holde pause ved faste tider, måles inaktivitet "
"ikke. I dette tilfælde er visse værdier i statistikken ikke særligt "
"informative."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The upper left block shows general statistics: some totals and some "
"information about idle time. The bottom left block shows something about "
"your work pace. You will see the total amount of activity since you started "
"the current log-in session. The amount of activity during some other "
"intervals will also be shown. The Pause Score decreases every time you skip "
"a break. The blocks to the right report on which short and long breaks have "
"already passed. At present, the labels in the dialog can either be black or "
"red and green. In the latter case a red statistic indicates a recommendation "
"to relax and take a break, which will bring the color closer to green."
msgstr ""
"Den øverste venstre gruppen viser almen statistik: nogle totalsummer og "
"statistikker over inaktivitet. Den nederste venstre gruppe viser noget om "
"din arbejdstakt. Du ser den totale aktivitet siden du begyndte at arbejde på "
"computeren (under sessionen), og desuden aktiviteten i nogle andre "
"intervaller. Pausescoringen mindskes hver gang du springer over en pause. "
"Grupperne til højre siger noget om de korte og lange pauser som allerede er "
"forbi. For øjeblikket kan etiketterne i dialogen være sorte, eller røde og "
"grønne. I det sidste tilfælde angiver rød statistik en anbefaling om at "
"slappe af og holde en pause, hvilket får farven til at nærme sig grønt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you right-click the tray icon, the context menu will show an option to "
"<guilabel>Suspend</guilabel> &rsibreak;. When you don't want to be "
"interrupted, such as during a game or a presentation, you can use this to "
"silence &rsibreak; You can resume &rsibreak; when you click right on the "
"icon again and select <guilabel>Resume</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Når du højreklikker på ikonen i statusfeltet, viser den sammenhængsafhængige "
"menu tilvalget <guilabel>Suspendér</guilabel> &rsibreak;. Når du ikke vil "
"afbrydes, såsom under et spil eller en præsentation, kan du bruge det til at "
"gøre &rsibreak; tavs. Du kan genaktivere &rsibreak; ved at højreklikke på "
"ikonen igen og vælge <guilabel>Genoptag</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Suspended &rsibreak;"
msgstr "&rsibreak; suspenderet"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "The tray icon when &rsibreak; is suspended"
msgstr "Ikonen i statusfeltet når &rsibreak; er suspenderet"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The last way to influence &rsibreak; is via &DCOP;. There are &DCOP; "
#| "commands available to force breaks and to suspend and resume &rsibreak;. "
#| "You can use these to suspend &rsibreak; automatically when you start a "
#| "game or any other specified program. Execute <command>dcop rsibreak "
#| "actions</command> to see the possibilities."
msgid ""
"The last way to influence &rsibreak; is via &DBus;. There are &DBus; "
"commands available to force breaks and to suspend and resume &rsibreak;. You "
"can use these to suspend &rsibreak; automatically when you start a game or "
"any other specified program. Execute <command>qdbus org.kde.rsibreak /"
"rsibreak</command> to see the possibilities."
msgstr ""
"Den sidste mulighed for at påvirke &rsibreak; er via &DCOP;. Der er &DCOP;-"
"kommandoer til at fremtvinge pauser, og lukke af og genoptage &rsibreak;. Du "
"kan bruge dem til automatisk at lukke af for &rsibreak; når du starter et "
"spil eller et hvilket som helst andet specificeret program. Kør "
"<command>dcop rsibreak actions</command> for at se mulighederne."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Break types"
msgstr "Pausetyper"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most settings are straightforward. On the general page, there is an option "
"to start up automatically at &kde; startup. You might wonder why that is "
"because the session manager should take care of that. Some users may need to "
"start &rsibreak; at startup while they are not using the session manager. "
"Note that <application>Gnome</application> will ignore the setting."
msgstr ""
"De fleste indstillinger er ganske lige til. På siden Generelt findes "
"tilvalget at starte automatisk når &kde; startes. Du kan undre dig over "
"hvorfor det behøves, eftersom sessionshåndteringen skulle sørge for det. "
"Visse brugere kan dog behøve at starte &rsibreak; når sessionshåndtering "
"ikke bruges. Bemærk at <application>Gnome</application> ignorerer denne "
"indstilling."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two behavior options in &rsibreak;. There is an option to break at "
"fixed intervals for fixed periods, and there is an option to reset the "
"timers when &rsibreak; detects that you have been idle for the duration of a "
"break."
msgstr ""
"Der er to tilvalg for hvordan &rsibreak; skal opføre sig. Der er mulighed "
"for at holde pause med faste intervaller i faste perioder, og der er "
"mulighed for at nulstille tidtagningen når &rsibreak; opdager at du er "
"uvirksom på tidspunktet  for en pause."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can indicate that you do not want RSIBreak to interfere with "
"presentations, games, video playback, and any other fullscreen application "
"on the current virtual desktop using the <guilabel>Suppress if fullscreen "
"windows present</guilabel> option."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "&rsibreak; popup"
msgstr "Meddelelse fra &rsibreak;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The lock button enables you to lock your screen whenever you leave your "
"computer"
msgstr ""
"Låseknappen gør det muligt at låse skærmen så snart du forlader computeren."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may find the full-screen notice to take a break inconvenient at the time "
"it appears. In this case, on the <guilabel>During Breaks</guilabel> page you "
"can indicate that you want to use a popup; a small popup near the tray will "
"appear asking you to take a break. If you choose to ignore that, the full-"
"screen activity-block will appear anyway."
msgstr ""
"Du synes måske at underretningen om at holde en pause som dækker hele "
"skærmen er upassende når den dukker op. I så tilfælde kan du angive at du "
"vil bruge en meddelelse på siden <guilabel>Under pauser</guilabel>. I dette "
"tilfælde vises en lille meddelelse udfor statusfeltet som beder dig om at "
"holde en pause. Hvis du vælger at ignorere den, vises underretningen som "
"dækker hele skærmen alligevel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There are two options for the full screen break. It can show a grid like "
#| "the &kde; logout screen (this is the default action), or a path may be "
#| "set up to specify a folder on your hard disk which contains images. "
#| "During a break, you will see a slideshow of those images."
msgid ""
"There are three options for the full screen break. It can show a "
"<guilabel>Complete Black Effect</guilabel> (this is the default action), "
"<guilabel>Show Plasma Dashboard</guilabel> or <guilabel>Show Slide Show of "
"Images</guilabel> where a path may be set up to specify a folder on your "
"hard disk which contains images. During a break, you will see a slideshow of "
"those images."
msgstr ""
"Der er to tilvalg for fuldskærmspauser. Den kan enten vise et gitter som "
"ligner &kde;'s udlogningsskærm (hvilket er standardopførsel), eller  en "
"søgesti til en mappe på harddisken som indeholder billeder kan indstilles. "
"Du ser så et lysbilledshow af disse billeder under en pause."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Duration/Interval of a break"
msgstr "Varighed eller interval for en pause"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&rsibreak; supports two different types of break: <quote>Tiny breaks</quote> "
"and <quote>Big breaks</quote>. The usual way to use these is to take "
"frequent tiny breaks, and occasional big breaks. For example, a break of 20 "
"seconds every 20 minutes (the tiny break), and a longer break of 2 minutes "
"every hour (the big break)."
msgstr ""
"&rsibreak; understøtter to forskellige slags pauser: <quote>korte pauser</"
"quote> og <quote>lange pauser</quote>. Den sædvanlige måde at bruge dem er "
"at tage hyppige korte pauser, og af og til lange pauser. En pause på 20 "
"sekunder hvert 20. minut (den korte pause), og en længere pause på 2 "
"minutter hver time (den lange pause)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "It is no use to set up intervals which are irritating. Those will, by "
#| "definition, get on your nerves and you will be more likely to hit &Esc; "
#| "&ndash; or any other key you have setup on the <guilabel>During breaks</"
#| "guilabel> page &ndash; to skip the break."
msgid ""
"It is no use to set up intervals which are irritating. Those will, by "
"definition, get on your nerves and you will be more likely to hit &Esc; "
"&ndash; or any other key you have setup on the <guilabel>During Breaks</"
"guilabel> page &ndash; to skip the break."
msgstr ""
"Der er ingen grund til at indstille intervaller som er irriterende. De går "
"dig på nerverne og det er troligt at du trykker på Esc, eller en anden tast "
"du har  indstillet på siden <guilabel>Under pauser</guilabel>, til at "
"springe over pausen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you find that you are often skipping breaks, you could decide to disable "
"the shortcut and hide the minimize button. Remember, you choose how strictly "
"to follow the break sequence."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du bemærker at du ofte springer over pauser, kan du bestemme dig for at "
"deaktivere genvejstasten og skjule minimeringsknappen. Husk at det er dig "
"som bestemmer hvor strengt du skal følge pausetiderne."

